OL,3,CMy Community: 130 groups creating
OL,4,Cbunting for 80th Liberation Day
OL,6,FThe organiser of Guernsey's Community
OL,7,FBunting Project says she has been
OL,8,Foverwhelmed by the response from
OL,9,Fislanders, with more than 130 groups
OL,10,Fnow involved.
OL,12,FThe St Peter Port Seafront will be
OL,13,Ffestooned with homemade decorations on
OL,14,F9 May 2025 to mark the 80th
OL,15,Fanniversary of the island's liberation
OL,16,Ffrom Nazi Occupation.
