OL,3,CMy Community: 130 groups creating
OL,4,Cbunting for 80th Liberation Day
OL,6,FMegs Bailey came up with the idea
OL,7,Fafter feeling frustrated at how
OL,8,FLiberation Day celebrations altered
OL,9,Fduring and after the Covid outbreak as
OL,10,Fmore smaller Parish events were
OL,11,Forganised, compared to the traditional
OL,12,Fgathering of crowds in central St
OL,13,FPeter Port where, in 1945, the
OL,14,FLiberation took place.
OL,16,FShe explains that the bunting honours
OL,17,Fthe 'make do and mend' ethos of the
OL,18,FOccupation when materials were hard to
OL,19,Fcome by.
