OL,6,F"By including everyone, those who are
OL,7,Flonely or isolated can join in,
OL,8,Ffriends can get together and new
OL,9,Ffriendships can be forged."
OL,11,FSince it started, Megs has heard
OL,12,Fstories of families being drawn
OL,13,Ftogether by the project, with
OL,14,Fgrandparents teaching grandchildren
OL,15,Fhow to sew.
OL,17,FOne woman is even taking her bunting
OL,18,Fbag to Australia to make a string of
OL,19,Fflags with her sister.
