OL,6,FMegs explains: "Feedback has been
OL,7,Fincredible. I have heard of UK expats
OL,8,Fcontacting their local families and
OL,9,Farranging a visit to get involved, new
OL,10,Fsocial groups coming together, people
OL,11,Fdusting off their sewing machines and
OL,12,Frenewing their love of sewing."
OL,14,FAnyone can get involved, either by
OL,15,Fdonating fabric or applying for a
OL,16,Fbunting bag.
