OL,3,CMy Community: 130 groups creating
OL,4,Cbunting for 80th Liberation Day
OL,6,FThe self-contained packs contain
OL,7,Finstructions, templates, fabric,
OL,8,Fthread and tape, together with a
OL,9,Fpersonalised flag so that people can
OL,10,Fidentify their own contribution when
OL,11,Fthe bunting is all assembled along the
OL,12,FSt Peter Port Seafront from La Salarie
OL,13,Fto the Slaughterhouse -possibly even
OL,14,Fbeyond if the surge of interest is
OL,15,Fanything to go by.
OL,17,FMegs adds: "The reactions of everyone
OL,18,Fwho is taking part has really been
OL,19,Fquite touching.
