OL,6,FMegs was interviewed as part of ITV
OL,7,FChannel's 'My Community Series' which
OL,8,Fcelebrates the importance of coming
OL,9,Ftogether - it can be a cookery class,
OL,10,Fa sports session, friends meeting up
OL,11,Fand much more.
OL,13,FTo share what community means to you,
OL,14,Fsend an email with the subject 'My
OL,15,FCommunity' to channelnews@itv.com with
OL,16,Fa few details about what you do and
OL,17,Fwhy it is so special so we can come
OL,18,Falong and hear all about it.
